text: Jane March (born 20 March 1973) is an English actress. She was born in London to a Vietnamese-Chinese mother and Anglo-Spanish father. She has starred in many movies. These movies include The Lover and Color of Night. Both of these movies were originally rated NC-17 by the MPAA. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Actors from London Category:English movie actors Category:1973 births Category:Living people
